I fall asleep? It was so painful...Huh? Those wings and horns, Dr Quang what happened to you??[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Dr Quang is just a fake identity. My name is Kai, i'm your Death's Messenger. [p]
You've reached your final moment and i'm here to give you a contract to make your final wish come true.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Hoang
You're kidding right?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
You know it better than anyone else. You already stopped breathing.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Hoang
Am i still dreaming?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
