B-But i already bought the ingredients to make the apple pie again.[p]
I thought i could make it right this time and let An enjoy it. I passed another test, i just haven't shown you guys the result yet. I already studied for the next exam.[p]
The heart operation is next week. I couldn't even live pass the 30 days due date with you guys. There are so much, so much things that i have yet to do...[p]
[_tb_end_text]

