#Hoang
I don't want to die. I'm scared. I'm so so scared. [p]
Please don't make me do this. [p]
I don't want to. I want to stay with you and An.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
I'm sorry, dear. There's no other way. [p]
Now you can either choose to make a contract with me for one final wish and disappear or continue to to the next life. [p]
This is your final judgement day[p]
[_tb_end_text]

